data.description:
*Please see Agent Notes* Don't miss this charming ranch home in the heart of Okolona. Located in a quiet neighborhood, this 3 bedroom 1 full bathroom home has been well maintained and boasts new appliances (2019 & 2021), new HVAC system (2020), new LVT and carpet flooring (2019), new driveway and porch (2021), new front windows (2022) and a new roof (2023). Along with these updates, the attic was also newly insulated in 2020! The living room opens to the dining room, providing the perfect space to entertain family or friends. The kitchen cabinets were painted and modernized to match the stainless steel appliances, with plenty of space in the kitchen for a coffee nook or rolling island. The large laundry room provides additional space for pantry
shelves and storage. The bedrooms are spacious and were painted in 2019. The newly sanded and painted deck is a great place to enjoy your morning coffee, overlooking the fully fenced, deep backyard. This home could be great for an investor or homeowner looking for an
affordable home with less maintenance risks. This home is also conveniently located near major highways, grocery stores, shopping, Jefferson Mall, and within walking distance to Target
shopping center. Join us at our Open House from 2pm - 4pm on 1/14. This home won't last long!
